We are creating a short survey to ask people which celebrities they think have the qualities which most embody the Games Maker criteria. Ideally I would see us adding a small box in the right hand column (below the 'When to apply' box and having a link to the survey in pop-up form: http://survey.london2012.com/survey/325729/2e11/

There is also some code which our survey tool has generated - I don't know if this would be any use:
